            "content": "<p>You can feel it even if you can't name it yet. The desire to create, to contribute, to become someone whose life actually reflects the greatness you know lives inside you.</p><p>This pull isn't random. It's your calling.</p><p><strong>and </strong><em><strong>your soul  has been trying to get your attention for a while now.</strong></em></p><p>It knows where you've been and it knows where you want to go. It holds the most accurate guidance you will ever receive.</p><p>My creations are designed to show you how to listen.</p><p>So you can finally hear what your soul has been trying to tell you. And the version of you that you have always felt stops feeling like a dream and starts feeling like a direction.</p>"
